            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Caterpillar搭上AI快車 出人意料成為市場贏家\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"582\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XCbxeGuvriag4E8SKxO8xA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/7080f580-9ffc-11f0-aeff-e9a8f283ec56\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Caterpillar搭上AI快車 出人意料成為市場贏家</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
