        {
            "title": "美國銀行體系準備金跌破3萬億美元大關之後進一步下降",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 美國銀行體系準備金連續第八周下降，跌破3萬億美元大關之後還在進一步向下。該指標為<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>決定繼續縮減資產負債表時的重要考量因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會周四公佈的數據顯示，截至10月1日當周，銀行準備金下降約201億美元，至2.98萬億美元，創1月份以來最低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：存放在聯儲會的銀行準備金跌破3萬億美元 美國財政部發債抽走流動性</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ck2mAb2pzlIGIaVosw84TQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fc614e97b0ab3f8f7a529fca88c152f9\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">準備金下降之際，美國財政部在7月債務上限上調後，加大了發債力度，以重建現金餘額。這抽走了聯儲會賬上其他負債的流動性，例如央行隔夜逆回購協議工具和銀行準備金。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a574c15a-dfab-33e6-b095-d969c2e99b74-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾上月表示，銀行準備金仍然充裕，預計縮表將在準備金達到充足水平時停止。然而，金融體系中的跡象表明，準備金可能正在接近這一水平，可能會迫使聯儲會結束縮表早於預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Bank Reserves Decline Further Below Key $3 Trillion Mark</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Carter Johnson.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E9%AB%94%E7%B3%BB%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E9%87%91%E8%B7%8C%E7%A0%B43%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%97%9C%E4%B9%8B%E5%BE%8C%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D-215501931.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-03 08:05:46",
